text: Goma Devi Timilsina is a CPN member and politician from Nepal (Unified Socialist). She was chosen in the Nepalese National Assembly election of 2022 and is a member of the Rashtriya Sabha as well. ==References== ==Other websites== *सदस्यहरु Category:Living people Category:Nepalese politicians
title: Goma Devi Timilsina
